Terror
Discworld ritual help
Terror

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Terror - Creating visions to invoke fear in your targets.
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Terror is an offensive ritual, which causes the target to relive a
childhood phobia, making them flee in terror.  You will require a
prayer book and a skull to perform this ritual.
.EP
